                    <callout1 type="arabic">Piston Cooling Jet</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Mounting Bolt</callout1>
                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
            <para>Remove the mounting bolt that secures each piston cooling jet to the crankcase. Remove the piston
                cooling jets.
            </para>
        </svcproc>
